flowchart TD
    A[Path + selected features S + instance x0] --> B[Build ordered selected-path CNF]
    B --> B1[selected-feature unit clauses]
    B --> B2[structural threshold order clauses]
    B --> B3[path branch clauses]
    B1 --> C{Classify CNF}
    B2 --> C
    B3 --> C
    C -->|Horn| D[Route to structural_horn backend]
    C -->|AntiHorn| E[Route to structural_antihorn backend]
    C -->|2-CNF| F[Route to two_sat backend]
    C -->|none| G[Raise NonTheoremPathError]
    D --> H[Record metadata]
    E --> H
    F --> H
    G --> H
    H --> H1[axp_backend]
    H --> H2[theorem_certified]
    H --> H3[path_certificate]
    H --> H4[theorem_mode_used]
    H --> H5[rejected_reason]
